An Act relating to counties; defining term; requiring
7
certain notification to board of county
8
commissioners; requiring publication of certain
8
notice; requiring certain public meetings; providing
9
for certain meeting of board of county commissioners;
9
requiring certain vote take place after certain
10
comment period; providing for codification; and
10
